## 1. Executive Summary

This specification defines the implementation of a centralized configuration management and preset system for VJLive3. It provides persistent storage, loading, and cloud synchronization of plugin parameters, project settings, and user preferences.

**Critical Objectives:**
- Save and restore complete plugin states (all parameters)
- Support project files with plugin configurations
- Enable cloud sync for cross-device preset sharing
- Provide CLI and UI for preset management
- Maintain backward compatibility with existing preset formats
- Ensure atomic save/load operations (no corruption)
- Support preset versioning and migration

