## 7. Performance Considerations

### 7.1 Save/Load Overhead

- **Save**: ~10-50ms for 50 plugins (JSON serialization + disk I/O)
- **Load**: ~10-50ms for 50 plugins (JSON parsing + param application)
- **Impact**: Blocking operation; show progress dialog in UI

### 7.2 Memory Usage

- Preset in memory: ~1KB per plugin (JSON as dict)
- 50 plugins → ~50KB (negligible)
- Projects larger (include metadata) → ~100KB

### 7.3 Optimization

- **Async I/O**: Use thread pool for disk operations in UI
- **Compression**: Optional gzip for large presets
- **Incremental save**: Only save changed plugins (future)

---

## 8. Security Considerations

### 8.1 Input Validation

- Validate preset schema before loading
- Sandbox plugin param values (type checking, range checking)
- Prevent path traversal in file operations

### 8.2 Cloud Security

- Encrypt credentials in config file
- Use OAuth tokens (not passwords)
- HTTPS only for cloud transfers
- User consent for cloud sync

