## 10. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Preset corruption on crash | High | Atomic writes (temp file + rename) |
| Schema changes break old presets | High | Versioning + migration scripts |
| Cloud sync conflicts | Medium | Last-write-wins with user notification |
| Slow save/load blocks UI | Medium | Async I/O with progress dialog |
| Malicious preset file | High | Schema validation; sandbox param values |
| Large presets consume memory | Low | Streaming JSON parser for huge projects |

